{"tid":329876,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獨家錄音揭斑馬牌受壓　停向良心雜貨店供貨","createTime":"2017-07-20T17:01:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T09:10:45.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"51f81c2bc8834afe70acb1a199e7e1597b85e2c5","tid":329876,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:01:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=_pv-FcsFy20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ffeature%3Dyoutu.be%26v%3D_pv-FcsFy20&d=H3R%2FOtjhShBos1YI6J9p%2BlKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=0ed7e086\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=_pv-FcsFy20</a><br />\nNextplus 壹週Plus 觀看次數：116<br />\n訂閱16.1萬<br />\n51<br />\n發佈日期：2017年7月20日開店至今，一直打著「平到好似執笠咁平」的旗號，專門賣平價雜貨的「執笠倉」，在全港有多間分店，去年在旺角金魚街再開一間，同時售賣文具，其文具售價較一般文具店和書局便宜。例如一支斑馬牌saraza筆，市價賣$8.5，他賣$7，並賣二送一。<br />\n<br />\n「執笠倉」老闆之一的蘇小姐指希望低收入的家庭和學生都能以可負擔的價錢購買生活用品，「香港仲有好多人生活係好邊緣既位置，其實如果你有能力，你可以用一個便宜一點的價錢賣給他們，何樂而不為？」<br />\n<br />\n不過，賣得便宜卻招來同行妒忌。去年，他們擬因受到在同一街道開店的老字號文具店陳湘記投訴，陳湘記向斑馬「詐型」，指「執笠倉」賣的文具「太便宜」，影響其生意以致蝕本。蘇小姐指，斑馬要求供貨予「執笠倉」的供應商東方文具即停止向「執笠倉」供貨。其後更索性不再跟東方文具簽新約，懷疑企圖打壓「執笠倉」。本刊獲得一段斑馬高級營業員馬先生與東方文具公司老闆七哥，於今年三月的電話錄音，顯示了斑馬不欲再供貨予執笠倉。<br />\n<br />\n記者致電陳湘記第三代接班人陳耀彰，他回應指不清楚旺角地鋪事件的來龍去脈，表示陳湘記只是家族生意，作風非常低調，暗示有人以「嘩眾取寵」的方式宣傳。「在這裡說是非的話呢，並非我們這些老字號的作風，我們是踏實低調的類型。」強調他們做好自己本份。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞︰<br />\n【文具情緣】七哥不怕得罪代理商 撐老婆平價賣文具<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2vBJHxG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2vBJHxG&d=H3R%2FOtjhShBos1YI6J9p%2BlKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=271df0fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2vBJHxG</a><br />\n<br />\n壹週Plus : <a href=\"http://hk.next.nextmedia.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.next.nextmedia.com&d=H3R%2FOtjhShBos1YI6J9p%2BlKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=71d97579\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.next.nextmedia.com&h=8070474f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.next.nextmedia.com</a><br />\n即 like 壹週Plus fb : <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/nextmagazinef...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnextmagazinef...&d=H3R%2FOtjhShBos1YI6J9p%2BlKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=d66b7c1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/nextmagazinef...</a><br />\n類別"},{"pid":"722d2734a1149dcd4b2f1fbe72e88c756a34cf1d","tid":329876,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:11:40.000Z","msg":"咁撚仆街"},{"pid":"8445e616dc7eeb60927a72cb025c8e78f2b7a945","tid":329876,"uid":81325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:18:19.000Z","msg":"召喚轉筆撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ac174782c8cd393b99bd24cf5ab50fbca8ae8a","tid":329876,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:23:03.000Z","msg":"陳湘記無耻！"},{"pid":"69f22646283e7bb20efd14b508d21d810257a046","tid":329876,"uid":31452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:25:47.000Z","msg":"759 2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec6054ebd60d737fd48173a04791bb52d46f0fa","tid":329876,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T17:39:50.000Z","msg":"當年曾經有 歌手 藝人 亮相亞視<br />\n結果畀TVB 打壓既打壓 封殺既封殺<br />\n<br />\n所以都唔怪得曬受壓既 唱片公司 經理人<br />\n唔肯供應歌手／唔派新歌 畀亞視😕"},{"pid":"6186d77c661407419551b5fd370a56baed355e6d","tid":329876,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T20:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5acfc9c878766505ef77d80340af9c687eedab38","tid":329876,"uid":42691,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T20:41:30.000Z","msg":"執笠倉搵快錢 轉頭就執笠<br />\n以本傷人玩謝行家<br />\n最後香港又少多幾間文具舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\